description: The "works_list" tool returns a list of work items based on specific filters. It supports filtering by parts, creators, issue priorities, Rev organizations, ownership, and stage names. Users can specify limits for the maximum number of works to return. This tool provides a comprehensive way to retrieve work items matching various criteria, enabling efficient management and tracking of work within the system.
examples:
Query 1: List work items created by user "JohnDoe".
Query 2: Retrieve work items with issue priority "High" and organization "Marketing".
Query 3: Show work items in stage "In progress" with owner "JaneSmith".
Query 4: Filter work items by part "Engine" and limit the maximum items to 20.
Query 5: Get work items created by user "Alice" and with issue priority "Critical".
Query 6: Display work items assigned to user "Bob" and in stage "Completed".
Query 7: List work items in organization "Sales" with issue priority "Low" and limit the maximum items to 10.
Query 8: Retrieve work items with issue priority "Medium" and ownership "TeamA".
Query 9: Show work items in stage "Pending review" with part "Software" and limit the maximum items to 15.
Query 10: Filter work items by organization "Operations" and creator "Sam" and show the first 5 items.

arguments.name: applies_to_part
arguments.description: Filters for work belonging to any of the provided parts

arguments.name: created_by
arguments.description: Filters for work created by any of these users

arguments.name: issue_priority
arguments.description: Filters for issues with any of the provided priorities. Allowed values: p0, p1, p2, p3

arguments.name: issue_rev_orgs
arguments.description: Filters for issues with any of the provided Rev organizations

arguments.name: limit
arguments.description: The maximum number of works to return. The default is '50'

arguments.name: owned_by
arguments.description: Filters for work owned by any of these users

arguments.name: stage_name
arguments.description: Filters for records in the provided stage(s) by name
